                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>By an exchange of notes signed at Washington, July 28 and August 28, 1954, and
                    entered into force on the latter date, the United States and Guatemala agreed to
                    extend and to amend the agreement of May 19, 1943, relating to the construction
                    of the Inter-American Highway in Guatemala. For the text of the notes, see 5 UST
                    (pt. 3) 2244, or TIAS No. 3084.</p>
            </div>
